{"id":2062,"date":"2021-05-10T22:16:15","date_gmt":"2021-05-10T11:16:15","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/synctech.com.au\/\/?post_type=ufaq&#038;p=2062"},"modified":"2022-01-31T21:03:05","modified_gmt":"2022-01-31T10:03:05","slug":"reduce-storage-used-by-backups","status":"publish","type":"ufaq","link":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/faqs\/reduce-storage-used-by-backups\/","title":{"rendered":"How do I reduce the amount of storage used by the backups?"},"content":{"rendered":"<style>.entry-header {\r\n    display: none;    \r\n}\r\n.single-ufaq .ewd-ufaq-faq-title {\r\n    display: none\r\n}\r\n.single-ufaq .ewd-ufaq-square &amp;amp;gt; span {\r\n    display: none;\r\n}\r\n.single-ufaq .ewd-ufaq-faq-body {\r\n    padding-left: initial;\r\n}\r\n.single-ufaq .ewd-ufaq-permalink {\r\n   display: none;\r\n}\r\n.single-ufaq .ewd-ufaq-back-to-top {\r\n   display: none;\r\n}<\/style><div  class=\"ewd-ufaq-faq-list ewd-ufaq-page-type-load_more\" id='ewd-ufaq-faq-list'>\n\n\t<input type='hidden' name='show_on_load' value='' id='ewd-ufaq-show-on-load' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='include_category' value='' id='ewd-ufaq-include-category' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='exclude_category' value='' id='ewd-ufaq-exclude-category' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='orderby' value='set_order' id='ewd-ufaq-orderby' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='order' value='asc' id='ewd-ufaq-order' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='post_count' value='-1' id='ewd-ufaq-post-count' \/>\n<input type='hidden' name='current_url' value='\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ufaq\/2062' id='ewd-ufaq-current-url' \/>\n\t\n\t\n\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-faqs'>\n\n\t\t<div  class=\"ewd-ufaq-faq-div ewd-ufaq-faq-column-count-one ewd-ufaq-faq-responsive-columns- ewd-ufaq-faq-display-style-default ewd-ufaq-can-be-toggled\" id='ewd-ufaq-post-2062-KjguelRMfj' data-post_id='2062'>\n\n\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-faq-title ewd-ufaq-faq-toggle'>\n\t\n\t<a class='ewd-ufaq-post-margin'  href='#' role=\"button\">\n\n\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-post-margin-symbol ewd-ufaq-square'>\n\t\t\t<span >A<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-faq-title-text'>\n\n\t\t\t<h4>\n\t\t\t\tHow do I reduce the amount of storage used by the backups?\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-clear'><\/div>\n\n\t<\/a>\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-faq-body ' >\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-post-margin ewd-ufaq-faq-post'>\n\t<p>The default setting in the app is to back up all the messages and call logs available on the phone at the time of the backup (Full backups). While this is a good option for quickly creating a new backup, it can quickly take up a lot of storage space if there are lots of messages and scheduled backups are used to created regular backups. There are a few different ways to reduce the storage:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Use a different backup type &#8211; create incremental backups or use archive mode. This can be changed from Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Backup settings &gt; Backup type. More info at\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/synctech.com.au\/\/faqs\/backup-types\/\">What are the backup types supported by the app?<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Only backup selected conversations. This can be done from Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Backup settings &gt; Selected conversations.<\/li>\n<li>Only backup messages sent\/received after a certain date. This can be done from Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Backup settings &gt; Withing date range.<\/li>\n<li>Set the app to automatically delete older backups. This setting is available for each of the cloud accounts supported and can be changed from the respective cloud settings screen at Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Backup location. For local backups, the app can be set to limit the storage used, this can be set from Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Backup location &gt; Retention.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-faq-custom-fields'>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-permalink'>\n\t\n\t<a href='https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/faqs\/reduce-storage-used-by-backups\/'>\n\t\t\n\t\tPermalink\t\t\t\n\t<\/a>\n\n<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class='ewd-ufaq-back-to-top'>\n\t\n\t<a class='ewd-ufaq-back-to-top-link'>\n\t\tBack to Top\t<\/a>\n\n<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A How do I reduce the amount of storage used by the backups? The default setting in the app is to back up all the messages and call logs available &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","ufaq-category":[3],"ufaq-tag":[],"class_list":["post-2062","ufaq","type-ufaq","status-publish","hentry","ufaq-category-general"],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ufaq\/2062","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ufaq"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/ufaq"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2062"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2062"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"ufaq-category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ufaq-category?post=2062"},{"taxonomy":"ufaq-tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.synctech.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ufaq-tag?post=2062"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}